OL,3,CDad accuses MOD of 'gross negligence'
OL,4,Cover soldier's military fitness test
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FPhillip Hoole spoke to ITV Border
OL,8,Fahead of handing in his petition to
OL,9,FDowning Street.
OL,11,FThe father of a soldier who died
OL,12,Fduring a military fitness test is
OL,13,Fcalling for the Ministry of Defence
OL,14,F(MoD) to be prosecuted for corporate
OL,15,Fmanslaughter.
OL,17,FPhillip Hoole is heading to Downing
OL,18,FStreet, to submit a petition and
OL,19,Fletter addressed to the Prime Minister.
