OL,3,CDad accuses MOD of 'gross negligence'
OL,4,Cover soldier's military fitness test
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FIt calls for the establishment of a
OL,8,Fnew regulatory body to oversee
OL,9,Finvestigations into institutional
OL,10,Ffailings, like the one he believes has
OL,11,Foccurred in the case of his son.
OL,13,FIn 2016 his son, Joshua, a 26-year-old
OL,14,Farmy corporal from Ecclefechan in
OL,15,FDumfries died whilst taking part in a
OL,16,Ffitness test in the Brecon Beacons.
