OL,7,FThe nineteenth of July 2016 was the
OL,8,Fhottest day of that year. Joshua Hoole
OL,9,Fand others were doing an Army Fitness
OL,10,FTest (AFT); an eight mile march
OL,11,Fcarrying 25 kilograms worth of kit
OL,12,Fthrough the Welsh Hills.
OL,14,FJust a few hundred metres from its
OL,15,Fend, Joshua, who was based at
OL,16,FCatterick Garrison and who had
OL,17,Fpreviously served in Afghanistan and
OL,18,FIraq, collapsed and died.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/11
