OL,4,Cover soldier's military fitness test
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"For the event they took part in the
OL,8,Fnormal dropout rate is 2.5%," Phillip
OL,9,Ftold ITV News. "On the day that Josh
OL,10,Fdied, the dropout rate was 40%. 18
OL,11,Findividuals out of 40 basically
OL,12,Fdropped out."
OL,14,FHe added that some soldiers needed
OL,15,Fmedical attention due to the intense
OL,16,Fheat, but said the test had carried on
OL,17,Fregardless and, he claims, in
OL,18,Fcontravention of army policy at the
OL,19,Ftime.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/11
