OL,4,Cover soldier's military fitness test
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"The AFT wasn't going to stop for any
OL,8,Freason, not even death," he said.
OL,9,F"Even after my son collapsed and died,
OL,10,Fthe remainder that were left still
OL,11,Ffinished the test."
OL,13,FPhillip was first told his son had
OL,14,Fdied due to Sudden Adult Death
OL,15,FSyndrome.
OL,17,FBut after fighting for a new inquest,
OL,18,Fa coroner in 2019 concluded that he
OL,19,Fhad died due to a high cardiovascular
OL,20,Fworkload following a combination of
OL,21,Fextreme heat and intense exercise.
