OL,7,FIn 2013 the same coroner had carried
OL,8,Fout an inquest into the deaths of
OL,9,Fthree soldiers who died in similar
OL,10,Fcircumstances to Joshua whilst
OL,11,Fattempting SAS selection.
OL,13,FAfter the inquest into Joshua Hoole's
OL,14,Fdeath, six years later, she said the
OL,15,Farmy had "failed" to learn from
OL,16,Fprevious mistakes, calling this
OL,17,F"deeply concerning."
