OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FHe added that in a meeting with a CPS
OL,8,Fprosecutor, he'd been told that the
OL,9,Fcase should have been looked at back
OL,10,Fin 2016.
OL,12,F"He actually admitted that I should
OL,13,Fnever have had to investigate my own
OL,14,Fson's death," Phillip said.
OL,16,FIn a statement, the Ministry of
OL,17,FDefence said: "Our thoughts and
OL,18,Fsympathies remain with Corporal Joshua
OL,19,FHoole's family and friends.
