OL,7,F"The coroner's inquest identified an
OL,8,Funderlying cardiac susceptibility as
OL,9,Fbeing the causal factor in Joshua's
OL,10,Fdeath. However, we recognise that heat
OL,11,Fcombined with strenuous exercise were
OL,12,Fsignificant contributory factors.
OL,14,F"This tragic event was rigorously
OL,15,Finvestigated by a Service Inquiry.
OL,16,FLessons and recommendations were
OL,17,Fidentified, and we've made a number of
OL,18,Fchanges and improvements to minimise
OL,19,Frisks to personnel."
